ss.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63773\">building for Android</a> by <a href=\"/Jon_Dart\" title=\"Jon Dart\">Jon Dart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 19, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Arasan\" title=\"Arasan\">Arasan</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64553\">Android build fails?</a> by <a href=\"/Rasmus_Althoff\" title=\"Rasmus Althoff\">Rasmus Althoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 07, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66273\">CT800 engine: Android problems?</a> by <a href=\"/Rasmus_Althoff\" title=\"Rasmus Althoff\">Rasmus Althoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 08, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/CT800\" title=\"CT800\">CT800</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69955\">understanding android chess engine binary formats</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mike_Adams&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mike Adams (page does not exist)\">Mike Adams</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70226\">create log on android</a> by <a href=\"/Pedro_Castro\" title=\"Pedro Castro\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 17, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Logging\" title=\"Logging\">Logging</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Android&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=7598